Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The My Lai massacre revealed, 1969
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yqk07
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 30 Nov 1969
The American reaction to hearing of the horror of the Son My massacre (My Lai) in Vietnam, and parallels with Hiroshima and the Allied devastation of Dresden.